    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p class="footer-copy">
        101, OM SQUARE, JADESHWAR, PARK, RANJIT SAGAR ROAD, JAMNAGAR GUJARAT INDIA 361005 | CIN:
        U46599GJ2026PTC172666
